
= xls_html_cleaner


== Description

Clean up your Excel generated HTML

== Installation

=== Archive Installation

	rake install

=== Gem Installation

	gem install xls_html_cleaner


== Features/Problems

 * remove not allowed `tags' ( not elements )
 * remove all attributes
 * remove comment
 * leave white spaces

If you give this script a non-html document, I don't know what happens :-)

== Synopsis

 $ xls_html_cleaner SRC_HTML > DEST_HTML
 $ cat SRC_HTML | xls_html_cleaner

